{"code":200,"status":"OK","data":{"number":175,"ayahs":[{"number":3675,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3675.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3675.mp3"],"text":"۞ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ أَنتُمُ ٱلْفُقَرَآءُ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ ۖ وَٱللَّهُ هُوَ ٱلْغَنِىُّ ٱلْحَمِيدُ","numberInSurah":15,"juz":22,"manzil":5,"page":436,"ruku":378,"hizbQuarter":175,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":35,"name":"سُورَةُ فَاطِرٍ","englishName":"Faatir","englishNameTranslation":"The Originator","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3676,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3676.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3676.mp3"],"text":"إِن يَشَأْ يُذْهِبْكُمْ وَيَأْتِ بِخَلْقٍۢ جَدِيدٍۢ","numberInSurah":16,"juz":22,"manzil":5,"page":436,"ruku":378,"hizbQuarter":175,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":35,"name":"سُورَةُ فَاطِرٍ","englishName":"Faatir","englishNameTranslation":"The Originator","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3677,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3677.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3677.mp3"],"text":"وَمَا ذَٰلِكَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ بِعَزِيزٍۢ","numberInSurah":17,"juz":22,"manzil":5,"page":436,"ruku":378,"hizbQuarter":175,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":35,"name":"سُورَةُ فَاطِرٍ","englishName":"Faatir","englishNameTranslation":"The Originator","revelationType":"Meccan"}},{"number":3678,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3678.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/3678.mp3"],"text":"وَلَا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌۭ وِزْرَ أُخْرَىٰ ۚ وَإِن تَدْعُ مُثْقَلَةٌ إِلَىٰ حِمْلِهَا لَا يُحْمَلْ مِنْهُ شَىْءٌۭ وَلَوْ كَانَ ذَا قُرْبَىٰٓ ۗ إِنَّمَا تُنذِرُ ٱلَّذِينَ يَخْشَوْنَ رَبَّهُم بِٱلْغَيْبِ وَأَقَامُوا۟ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ ۚ وَمَن تَزَكَّىٰ فَإِنَّمَا يَتَزَكَّىٰ لِنَفْسِهِۦ ۚ وَإِلَى ٱللَّهِ ٱلْمَصِيرُ","numberInSurah":18,"juz"